pageContext.claim: “The last 47 years, sleepy Joe Biden who shipped away your jobs, shut down your factories, threw open your borders, and ravaged our cities while sacrificing American blood and treasure in these ridiculous, endless foreign wars of countries that you've never even heard about, right?  You've never even heard their name. So sad. They're all coming back, you know that. Joe Biden is a servant of the globalists, and the lobbyists, and the wealthy donors, the people that I could be calling.”
pageContext.analysis: This is ridiculous over-the-top rhetoric, a smear on hyperdrive.
